1:
Yahweh, do not rebuke me in your anger;
\q do not punish me in your wrath.
\q

3:
My whole body is sick because of your anger;
\q there is no health in my bones because of my sin.
\q

7:
For within me, I am filled with burning;
\q there is no health in my flesh.
\q

11:
My friends and companions shun me because of my condition;
\q my neighbors stand far off.
\q

13:
But I, I am like a deaf man and hear nothing;
\q I am like a mute man who says nothing.
\q

15:
Surely I wait for you, Yahweh;
\q you will answer, Lord my God.
\q

19:
But my enemies are numerous;
\q those who hate me wrongfully are many.
\q

21:
Do not abandon me, Yahweh;
\q my God, do not stay far away from me.
\q
